aw]], [[Keri Russell]]\n|MusicalGuests=[[Fall Out Boy]]\n|ShortSummary=Hard [[GED]] Questions; Questlove's birthday; ''Tonight Show'' Pros & Cons: Obama's [[State of the Union address|State of the Union Address]]; Jimmy promotes [[MasterCard]] Priceless Surprises; Inflatable Flip Cup (Keri Russell); Fall Out Boy performed \"[[Centuries (song)|Centuries]]\"\n|LineColor=42612C\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=199\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|1|21}}\n|Guests=[[Jennifer Aniston]], [[Bill Gates]], [[Mario Batali]]\n|MusicalGuests={{TableTBA|N/A}}\n|ShortSummary=Millennial Changes; ''Tonight Show'' Lip Flip (Jennifer Aniston); Bill Gates brings Jimmy a cap and bumper sticker; Bill Gates and Jimmy drink water made from sewage\n|LineColor=42612C\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=200\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|1|22}}\n|Guests=[[Blake Shelton]], [[Bob Costas]]\n|MusicalGuests=[[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]]\n|ShortSummary=Hot Sax; [[Roger Wicker]] Quotes; ''Tonight Show'' Splittin' the Diff; ''Tonight Show'' #hashtags: #MyTouchdownDance; ''Tonight Show'' Whisper Challenge (Blake Shelton); M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce performed \"[[Girls, Girls, Girls (M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce song)|Girls, Girls, Girls]]\"\n|LineColor=42612C\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=201\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|1|23}}\n|Guests=[[Ryan Seacrest]], [[Taraji P. Henson]]\n|MusicalGuests=[[Maddie & Tae]]\n|ShortSummary=Joe Biden Faces; Putin voice-over; Thank You Notes; Charades (Jimmy Fallon & Ryan Seacrest Vs. Tariq & Taraji P. Henson); Maddie & Tae performed \"[[Fly (Maddie & Tae song)|Fly]]\"\n|LineColor=42612C\n}}\n}}\n\n===February===\n{{episode table|overall=4|airdate=17|guests=40|musicalguests=25|background=006080|episodes=\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=Special\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|2|1}}\n|Guests=[[Will Ferrell]], [[Kevin Hart]], [[Super Bowl XLIX|Super Bowl Champion]] [[2014 New England Patriots season|New England Patriots]]\n|MusicalGuests=[[Ariana Grande]]\n|Sho