ne]], [[Steven Yeun]]\n|MusicalGuests=[[Chris Brown]]\n|ShortSummary=Clintons' Speaking Engagements; ''Tonight Show'' Superlatives; Jimmy promotes [[State Farm Insurance]] Discount Double Check; Jimmy gives Nathan Lane a blanket; ''Tonight Show'' Kid Dictionary (Nathan Lane); Chris Brown performed \"[[Zero (Chris Brown song)|Zero]]\"\n|LineColor=F4CA16\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=376\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|11|26}}\n|Guests=[[Queen Latifah]], [[Rashida Jones]], [[Daniel Humm|Chef Daniel Humm]]\n|MusicalGuests={{TableTBA|N/A}}\n|ShortSummary=More Accurate Instagram Captions; [[Kool Keith]] sits in with The Roots; Bird Flu (appearance by [[Larry Bird]]); Thank You Notes; Rashida Jones and Jimmy sing holiday versions of songs (appearance by Queen Latifah, [[Eric Nally]])\n|LineColor=F4CA16\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=377\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|11|30}}\n|Guests=[[J. J. Abrams]], [[Pink (singer)|Pink]]\n|MusicalGuests=[[The Flaming Lips]]\n|ShortSummary=[[Black Friday (shopping)|Black Friday]] Poll; Black Friday Deals; The Roots do jokes about the [[Philadelphia 76ers]]; Obama Poem; [[Mindi Abair]] sits in with The Roots; ''Tonight Show'' Do Not Read; The Flaming Lips performed \"[[Clouds Taste Metallic|Bad Days]]\"\n|LineColor=F4CA16\n}}\n}}\n\n===December===\n{{episode table|overall=4|airdate=17|guests=40|musicalguests=25|background=FF549F|episodes=\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=378\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|12|1}}\n|Guests=[[Harrison Ford]], [[Seth MacFarlane]]\n|MusicalGuests=[[JoJo (singer)|JoJo]]\n|ShortSummary=[[Marco Rubio]] Comedy Special Advertisement; ''Tonight Show'' Pros & Cons: Holiday Season in NYC; The Yahoo! Answers Lounge Singers (Seth MacFarlane); Harrison Ford and Jimmy have a drink; Jimmy shows Harrison Ford a spit take; JoJo performed \"[[When Love Hurts]]\"\n|LineColor=FF549F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=379\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|12|2}}\n|Guests=[[Adam Driver]], [[Brett Favre