aprio]] Quote; David Schwimmer Phone Call; Jimmy counts down top/bottom songs in the country; ''Tonight Show'' Audience Suggestion Box (Tariq raps about the Republican candidates, Reba McEntire and Jimmy serenade audience member); Sir Ben Kingsley takes audience member's cell phone; Reba McEntire performed \"Until They Don't Love You\"\n|LineColor=979797\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=312\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|8|13}}\n|Guests=[[Paul Giamatti]], [[Alicia Vikander]]\n|MusicalGuests=[[Robin Thicke]]\n|ShortSummary=Crew Sketches; Steve Higgins' birthday; Freestylin' with The Roots; Alicia Vikander teaches Jimmy a dance; Jimmy gives Alicia Vikander [[IKEA]] party package; Robin Thicke performed \"[[Back Together (Robin Thicke song)|Back Together]]\"\n|LineColor=979797\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=313\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|8|14}}\n|Guests=[[Kevin Spacey]], [[Keegan-Michael Key]]\n|MusicalGuests=Monroe Martin\n|ShortSummary=Scott Walker Can't Say \"Volume\"; Thank You Notes; Kevin Spacey plays harmonica; Phone Booth (Kevin Spacey)\n|LineColor=979797\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=314\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|8|17}}\n|Guests=[[Zac Efron]], [[Fran Lebowitz]]\n|MusicalGuests=The cast of ''[[Amazing Grace (musical)|Amazing Grace]]''\n|ShortSummary=Pony Statements; ''Tonight Show'' Screengrabs; Egg Russian Roulette (Zac Efron); the cast of ''Amazing Grace'' performed \"[[Amazing Grace]]\"\n|LineColor=979797\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=315\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2015|8|18}}\n|Guests=[[Taraji P. Henson]], [[Edward Burns]]\n|MusicalGuests=[[Sam Hunt (musician)|Sam Hunt]]\n|ShortSummary=[[Sharon Jones (singer)|Sharon Jones]] sits in with The Roots; ''Tonight Show'' Pros & Cons: ''Sesame Street'' Moving to [[HBO]]; Jimmy promotes [[Ford Focus]] ST (appearance by [[Brad Keselowski]]); ''Tonight Show'' Fast ''Family Feud'' (Taraji P. Henson); Sam Hunt performed \"[[House Party (Sam Hunt song)|House Party]]\"\n|Lin